---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import StoryStep from '../StoryStep.astro';
import Canvas from '../Canvas.astro';
import Item from '../Item.astro';
import skyline from '../../assets/your-move/skyline.png';
---

<StoryStep title="Your Move" mediaFirst>
	<Canvas slot="media" fill fitScale="height" class="cluster">
		<Item left="0.2%" top="8.4%" width="100%">
			<Image src={skyline} alt="The Atlanta skyline" />
		</Item>
	</Canvas>

	<div class="copy">
		<p>
			Atlanta has been stolen, built, burned, and rebuilt—over and over. None of
			it was inevitable. Every version was built by someone who believed the city
			could be more.
		</p>
		<p>
			It's still unfinished. The next sound hasn't dropped. The next reinvention
			hasn't been built yet. It's your turn to embrace the Atlanta spirit.
		</p>
	</div>
</StoryStep>

<style>
	/* breathing room below the body text, before the prev/next bar */
	.copy {
		padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	/* more gap between the canvas and the copy on phone */
	:global(:root[data-bp='phone']) .copy {
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}
</style>
